  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074940/extras/0642fc7fce18223a0dac0ad776503159.webp?t=1772416511\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>In order to make up for the corruption committed by her father, Silvia had to help the development of the border city as an alchemist.<br>But if she wants to use alchemy, she must convert the spiritual power of residents into energy.<br><br>To shoulder the mission, Silvia collected spiritual power while using Alchemy to enrich people's lives.<br>However, after gaining the recognition of the residents, Silvia accidentally discovered the [truth] of alchemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074940/extras/988a4aff11e4d06fc8091ce64493e363.webp?t=1772416511\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>JRPG<br></li><li>Turn-Based command battle<br></li><li>Crafting system</li></ul>",
